Download TIGER shapes for Combined Statistical Area

Source: R/csa.R
tt_csa.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Combined Statistical Area

Usage

tt_csa(year = 2021)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_csa()
